<br>
<br>
&quot;The unthinkable had been accomplished, the impossible realized. Hidden from the sight of the gods, a lone rogue had infiltrated the citadel and stolen something so precious, something so rare, that many of the gods were as close to panic as gods can be. Never before had a mortal approached, much less entered, the citadel of the gods unbidden. Never before had an atrocity such as this been visited upon the gods.  Never before had the sanctity of the citadel been violated. Such was the travesty now before the assembled pantheon, eternal differences temporarily cast aside to resolve the tragedy before them.<br>
<br>
The Golden Dragon, Elorinur, wept tears of flaxen colored blood. Her sole egg, laid once every 10,000 years, had been stolen. As leader of the Celestial Mounts, those dragons that carried the gods across time and                        space, Elorinur's grief was felt throughout the ranks...all Mounts grieved with her, refusing to take flight.<br>
How could this be?  Veeshan herself had enveloped the egg in a cocoon of the purest magic, even from her deep slumber in the Plane of Sky, promising the rare hatching of a great and powerful dragon.  The loss of any Dragon's egg, let alone one promising a dragon of such immense power, was an event unheard of. All eggs were guarded, kept safe in the brood dens specifically created for them. A legion of Storm Guards stood watch over the den, and even now, the blood of many a Guard flowed as the gods vented their rage.<br>
<br>
Innoruuk, standing away from the other gods in a corner of the Great Hall, seethed with hate, silent...&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
Hear ye this, all Norrathians on the Brell Serilis server!  The above excerpt taken from our histories was shared with you at our most desperate hour.  We, the blessed monks of the Zan Fi, beseech your help in tracking this audacious rogue and recovering the lost egg of Elorindur.  Quellious herself, in a vision sent to our sensei Jagriel, instructed us to search for the rogue and return with information regarding the theft, but we have been thwarted in our attempts.  We now fear that our ranks have been infiltrated by cohorts in the conspiracy!  We call out to those of you brave enough, smart enough and daring enough to aid us in our efforts, and preserve tranquility and order in the world of Norrath.  We offer as a reward to the successful party the total sum of our meager guild treasury, 2500 platinum pieces, as a small incentive to aid us in this greatest of tasks.<br>
<br>
Please visit our monastery at www.zanfi.com and enter the garden of discussion to learn the entire history and codes of conduct, and to announce you and your party's brave intention to solve this unholy mystery.  Speed be with you, for the great search begins this Saturday, the 15th of April, at the auspicious hour of 6 PM, Pacific Standard Time.<br>
<br>
May Quellious be with you all.<br>
<br>
The Zan Fi Monks of Brell Serilis <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showMessage?topicID=27.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showMessage?topicID=17.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.threadControl?topicID=29.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=29.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=29.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm48">Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisfrm56">Salutations & Congratulations <option value="brellserilisfrm33">Dreams & Diversions (Off Topic)<option value="brellserilisfrm55">Fellowship of Guilds (Guildchat)<option value="brellserilisbrellslairadminonly">Brell's Lair (Admin only)<option value="brellserilisfrm64">Archived Threads<option value="brellserilismeleetalk">Tome: Races and Classes <option value="brellserilisroleplaying">Tome: History of Norrath<option value="brellserilisfrm49">Tome: Visions of Norrath<option